Class ToolbarGroupView

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hoverable, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChartButtonsPanel, EditButtonsPanel, ExportButtonPanel, PlanningPokerButtonsPanel, RequirementButtonsPanel

    public class ToolbarGroupView
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements Hoverable
    Holds a view for a group of controls on the toolbar. The group has a name, which is displayed in a label on the bottom, and content, which is displayed above. Clients should make sure to set preferred/minimum/maximum sizes appropriately in order to best fit their contents.
